    "content": "<p>\"It is possible to resurrect the mortal Iomedae,\" she says without disabusing him of the fairly ridiculous notion that he could in some way have spared Her the cost of telling him that. It would in fact be a waste of their shared resources to say that.&nbsp;</p>",
