    "id": 2047696,
    "content": "<p>&hellip;That one might in fact not be his (or Lastwall&rsquo;s) fault though if they&rsquo;ve been able to resurrect the mortal Iomedae this whole time - well <em>someone</em> made a mistake somewhere in there. He teleports to Vigil as soon as the vision ends, to ask Her in the next planned <em>commune</em> whether this vision was in fact from Her, then does a <em>sending</em> to ask, ugh, Clepati, whether she happens to have prepared <em>true resurrection</em> this morning.</p>",
